<hack name="Improved Programmable Lift" author="SlightlyIntelligentMonkey">
	<panel>
		<field type="label">NPC 025</field>
		<field type="info">
		 A better version of the Egg Corridor Lift (NPC 25).
		 It has 3 states, off (0), one where it goes up and then goes down (1),
		 and one where it goes up twice then down twice (2). 
		 You can choose how many frames (distance) it goes up or down with
		 the direction variable when setting the ANP.
